<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 15:15:12 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>阿斯利康：在与政府谈判期间正在审查在英国的4.5亿英镑投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-450-million-pound-investment-uk-under-review-amid-talks-with-govt-2024-11-12/</link><description>伦敦上市制药商阿斯利康表示，其 3 月份宣布的在英国投资 4.5 亿英镑（5.767 亿美元）用于疫苗研发的计划正在接受审查，同时与政府就激励措施进行谈判仍在继续。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 14:32:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-450-million-pound-investment-uk-under-review-amid-talks-with-govt-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>沙特队期待雷纳德重拾昔日辉煌，重燃世界杯挑战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/saudis-look-renard-recapture-past-glories-reignite-world-cup-challenge-2024-11-12/</link><description>周四，沙特阿拉伯将在墨尔本举行的亚洲世界杯预选赛中迎战澳大利亚队，希望重燃昔日的辉煌，绿猎鹰队的目标是随着埃尔维·雷纳德的回归，摆脱罗伯托·曼奇尼时代的低迷状态。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 14:23:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/saudis-look-renard-recapture-past-glories-reignite-world-cup-challenge-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>盈利和中国担忧拖累富时 100 指数跌至三个月低点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/earnings-china-worries-drag-ftse-100-three-month-low-2024-11-12/</link><description>由于担心唐纳德·特朗普可能任命对华鹰派为美国首席外交官，以及一些令人失望的企业最新消息，伦敦基准指数周二触及三个多月来的最低点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 13:35:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/earnings-china-worries-drag-ftse-100-three-month-low-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>阿斯利康称被拘留的中国区负责人有律师，但公司仍处于黑暗之中</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-ceo-says-detained-china-chief-has-lawyer-we-have-no-information-2024-11-12/</link><description>阿斯利康首席执行官周二表示，上个月被中国当局拘留的阿斯利康中国区总裁王立峰正在与律师联系，但该公司对此案的信息很少。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 13:12:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-ceo-says-detained-china-chief-has-lawyer-we-have-no-information-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>伊拉克入围 11 家公司参与 Grand Faw 港口运营，将于 2025 年 1 月做出决定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iraq-shortlists-11-firms-grand-faw-port-operation-decision-january-2025-2024-11-12/</link><description>伊拉克港口总公司总经理周二对路透表示，伊拉克已入围 11 家航运公司竞逐 Grand Faw 港口运营合同，预计将于 2025 年 1 月决定获胜者。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 11:48:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iraq-shortlists-11-firms-grand-faw-port-operation-decision-january-2025-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲股市因中国担忧和业绩不佳而承压</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/european-shares-under-pressure-china-worries-downbeat-earnings-2024-11-12/</link><description>欧洲股市周二下跌，因担心唐纳德·特朗普可能任命对华鹰派为美国最高外交官，与中国相关的权重股跌幅居前，而一些悲观的业绩加剧了跌幅。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 11:44:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/european-shares-under-pressure-china-worries-downbeat-earnings-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国珠海发生肇事逃逸事件 35人死亡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/thirty-five-people-killed-hit-and-run-incident-zhuhai-china-2024-11-12/</link><description>据国家电视台中央电视台周二报道，周一晚间，一辆汽车在中国南部城市珠海的一个体育中心外冲撞一群人，造成 35 人死亡、43 人受伤。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 11:02:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/thirty-five-people-killed-hit-and-run-incident-zhuhai-china-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：比特币：达到 90,000 美元及以上？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-11-12/</link><description>达拉·拉纳辛格 (Dhara Ranasinghe) 展望美国和全球市场未来一天</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 11:02:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>拜登任期结束，美国对石油和天然气排放者征收甲烷费</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/us-sets-methane-fee-oil-gas-emitters-biden-term-winds-down-2024-11-12/</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登政府周二敲定了向大型石油和天然气生产商征收甲烷费，旨在削减这种强大的温室气体的排放量，但唐纳德·特朗普就任总统后可能会废除这一收费。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 10:02:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/us-sets-methane-fee-oil-gas-emitters-biden-term-winds-down-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>世贸组织可能会在特朗普就任总统之前寻求重新任命主席</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/wto-hold-special-meeting-end-nov-weigh-chiefs-reappointment-2024-11-12/</link><description>周二的一份文件显示，世界贸易组织计划在本月晚些时候召开最高决策机构特别会议，会上可能会重新任命总干事恩戈齐·奥孔乔-伊韦阿拉。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 09:54:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/wto-hold-special-meeting-end-nov-weigh-chiefs-reappointment-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>珠海航展开幕，中国商飞订单及未来航天飞机一睹风采</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/zhuhai-air-show-opens-with-orders-comac-glimpse-future-spaceplane-2024-11-12/</link><description>中国的航空航天雄心在第一天成为焦点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 09:48:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/zhuhai-air-show-opens-with-orders-comac-glimpse-future-spaceplane-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，北京推动加入保障巴基斯坦公民安全的努力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/beijing-pushes-join-security-efforts-citizens-pakistan-sources-say-2024-11-12/</link><description>消息人士称，在卡拉奇发生被视为重大安全漏洞的汽车爆炸事件后，北京在会谈中敦促巴基斯坦允许本国安全人员为在这个南亚国家工作的数千名中国公民提供保护。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 09:18:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/beijing-pushes-join-security-efforts-citizens-pakistan-sources-say-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国航空工业集团公司在珠海航展上展示无人货运飞机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinas-avic-reveals-uncrewed-cargo-spaceplane-zhuhai-air-show-2024-11-12/</link><description>国有航天公司中航工业周二在中国最大的珠海航展上推出了中国第一架商用无人驾驶航天飞机，其任务是为中国空间站提供补给。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 08:42:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinas-avic-reveals-uncrewed-cargo-spaceplane-zhuhai-air-show-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>COP29东道主阿塞拜疆猛烈抨击西方捍卫石油和天然气工业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/cop29-pay-up-or-face-climate-led-disaster-humanity-warns-un-chief-2024-11-12/</link><description>今年联合国气候峰会的主办国阿塞拜疆总统周二猛烈抨击了西方对其国家石油和天然气行业的批评。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 08:20:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/cop29-pay-up-or-face-climate-led-disaster-humanity-warns-un-chief-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>印度动力煤进口量创15个月以来最大跌幅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-thermal-coal-imports-fall-fastest-pace-15-months-2024-11-12/</link><description>数据分析公司 Bigmint 和 Kpler 的数据显示，由于发电放缓和清洁能源产量增加，10 月份印度动力煤进口量同比下降约三分之一。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 07:37:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-thermal-coal-imports-fall-fastest-pace-15-months-2024-11-12/</guid></item></channel></rss>